title: Basic Concepts in Biochemistry - a students survival guide
description:
Basic Concepts in Biochemistry - a students survival guide
by Hiram Gilbert
McGraw-Hill Medical, 2nd ed. 1999
PDF

Unlike conventional texts or review books that stress memorizing facts, BASIC CONCEPTS stresses the mastering of fundamental concepts, so that the reader truly comprehends the material and feels comfortable applying it. Dr. Gilbert uses simple, jargon-free language and award-winning teaching techniques including algorithms, mnemonics and clinical examples.
